	Document(content="Question: I am working through the last function of Problem 2 and I keep finding that the corresponding value in index of 'ion' seems to be higher than the 'sec'. Is this correct or am I misunderstanding something here? Thanks in advance! Answer: If this is for 1_vidText.txt and you are referring to the tf-idf score of sec and ion, then that would not be right, since the most distinctive/unique n-gram in 1_vidText.txt is 'sec' (as in the example output), which will have the highest tf-idf score of the n-grams in the file. ", meta={'folders': ['hw8'], 'title': 'HW8 Problem 2 Find_Dinstinc_Ngrams Function', 'timestamp': '2022-11-11T16:20:54Z', 'user': '', 'tags': ['hw8', 'student'], 'likes': 0, 'views': 128}),
