	Document(content="Question: I have already found the value for the test, but I got a really small value of #e-48. Is this value reasonable or way too small. The number just doesn't seem right and I wanted to double check. Answer: This is a reasonable value. The p-value and standard score are inversely related. A large standard score magnitude will result in a small p-value and vice versa. ", meta={'folders': ['hw5'], 'title': 'HW 5 Probelm One Question Part 5 E.', 'timestamp': '2022-10-01T17:03:18Z', 'user': 'ktnb8chh43f2xw', 'tags': ['hw5', 'student'], 'likes': 0, 'views': 137}),
